title>WebP.run — Video to Animated WebP Converter</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Convert video to lightweight animated WebP images — instantly, in your browser. No uploads. No tracking. Just fast, private WebP conversion with smart defaults.\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"WebP.run\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"webp,video converter,animated webp,gif alternative,web performance,image optimization\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"WebP.run — Video to Animated WebP Converter\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Convert video to lightweight animated WebP — instantly, in your browser.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://webp.run\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"WebP.run\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"WebP.run — Video to Animated WebP Converter\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Convert video to lightweight animated WebP — instantly, in your browser.\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/a6dad97d9634a72d.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"gradient-bg min-h-screen\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"noise-overlay\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-bg-primary\"><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 glass border-b border-border-subtle\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-px glow-line\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between h-14\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-bg-primary font-bold text-sm\">W</span></div><span class=\"font-semibold text-text-primary group-hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors\">WebP.run</span></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-6\"><a class=\"text-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/convert\">Converter</a><a class=\"text-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/email\">Email</a><a class=\"text-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/webflow\">Webflow</a><a class=\"text-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/framer\">Framer</a><a class=\"text-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/shopify\">Shopify</a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><a class=\"btn-secondary text-sm py-1.5 px-3 rounded-lg\" href=\"/pro\">Unlock Pro</a></div></div></div></header><main class=\"pt-24 pb-20\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4\">Privacy Policy</h1><p class=\"text-text-secondary mb-8\">Last updated: December 2024</p><div class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8\"><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4\">Our Commitment to Privacy</h2><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed\">WebP.run is built with privacy as a core principle. We believe your files are your business, not ours. This policy explains how we handle (or rather, don&#x27;t handle) your data.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4\">Client-Side Processing</h2><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4\">All video conversion happens entirely in your browser using WebAssembly technology. This means:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4\"><li>Your video files never leave your device</li><li>No files are uploaded to our servers</li><li>We cannot see, access, or store your content</li><li>Processing works offline after initial page load</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4\">Data We Collect</h2><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4\">We collect minimal data to operate and improve the service:</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-medium text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3\">Analytics (Optional)</h3><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed\">We may use privacy-focused analytics to understand how the tool is used. This includes page views, feature usage patterns, and general geographic region. No personal identifiers are collected.</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-medium text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3\">Pro Purchases</h3><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed\">If you purchase Pro, payment processing is handled by our payment provider. We receive confirmation of purchase but do not store payment details. Your Pro status is stored locally in your browser.</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-medium text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3\">Local Storage</h3><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed\">We use browser local storage to remember your preferences and Pro status. This data never leaves your device.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4\">Data We Don&#x27;t Collect</h2><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4\"><li>Your video files or any processed content</li><li>Personal information unless you make a purchase</li><li>Tracking cookies for advertising</li><li>Data for sale to third parties</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4\">Third-Party Services</h2><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4\">We use the following third-party services:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4\"><li><strong>FFmpeg WASM</strong> — Open-source video processing library loaded from CDN</li><li><strong>Payment Provider</strong> — For processing Pro purchases (if applicable)</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4\">Cookies</h2><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed\">We use essential cookies only. No advertising or tracking cookies. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect preference saving.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4\">Your Rights</h2><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4\">Since we don&#x27;t collect personal data, most data rights requests don&#x27;t apply. However:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4\"><li>You can clear local storage to remove all preferences</li><li>You can use the tool without any data collection by disabling JavaScript analytics</li><li>Contact us if you have questions about your data</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4\">Changes to This Policy</h2><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed\">We may update this policy occasionally. Significant changes will be announced on the site. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4\">Contact</h2><p class=\"text-text-secondary leading-relaxed\">Questions about privacy? Email us at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:privacy@webp.run\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline\">privacy@webp.run</a></p></section></div></div></div></main><footer class=\"border-t border-border-subtle bg-bg-secondary/50\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 mb-10 pb-10 border-b border-border-subtle\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4 text-accent-primary\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">100% client-side processing</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4 text-accent-primary\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">No data uploads</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-4 h-4 text-accent-primary\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"></polygon></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">No account required</span></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-10\"><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-medium text-text-primary mb-4\">Product</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-sm text-text-tertiary hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors\" href=\"/convert\">Converter</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-text-tertiary hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors\" href=\"/pro\">Pro Features</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-text-tertiary hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors\" href=\"/guides\">Guides</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-medium text-text-primary mb-4\">Use Cases</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-sm text-text-tertiary hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors\" href=\"/email\">Email Marketing</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-text-tertiary hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors\" href=\"/webflow\">Webflow</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-text-tertiary hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors\" href=\"/framer\">Framer</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-text-tertiary hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors\" href=\"/shopify\">Shopify</a></li></ul></